overview: The Ten Commandments of Successful Duck Hunting is a step-by-step guide of proven tactics assembled by the Duckmen of Louisiana. The commandments they preach have helped other duck hunters become an authority in waterfowl hunting, and it will help you put more ducks in your blind. Featuring Phil Robertson and the rest of the Duckmen as they discuss the ins and outs of what makes them successful duck hunters.
title: 10 Commandments for Successful Duck Hunting
